161
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,560
-Okay.
-Good job, everyone.

162
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,700
Thank you.

163
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:09,040
We had a great time today, Chef.

164
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:10,990
So did I.

165
00:11:11,590 --> 00:11:14,260
