178
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:50,870
Let me help. It's a lot to do by yourself.

179
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:55,270
No. It's more convenient for me
to do it by myself.

180
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:04,470
Is everything okay with you?

181
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:07,420
Yes, everything's fine.

182
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,690
That's good.

183
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,920
