211
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:34,090
I know it's just a rumor, so don't worry.

212
00:13:34,530 --> 00:13:38,930
I just want to tell you that
this could be an option for you.

213
00:13:39,650 --> 00:13:40,230
I know.

214
00:13:40,230 --> 00:13:41,900
